Name: Average time from Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE to Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: Average time between Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER and Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Total time for cases ending with Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER
Metric: The sum of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: Minimum time to Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER from Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: Average resolution time of Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER and the end of the case

Name: Total resolution time of cases involving Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER and the end of the case

Name: Average time from Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER to Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE for re-submission
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Minimum time between Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER and next Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time from Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION to Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: Average waiting time to Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER after Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: Total time it takes Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER to be followed by Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Average time it takes from Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER to Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Minimum resolution time of cases with Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER followed by Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: Average time from Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER to Request Payment in cases where it is eventually approved
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Total time for Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER cycle in cases where it leads to case closure without approval
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER and the end of the case
